			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-12 columns">
			<p></p>
			<p class="text-center"><img src="/img/theme/logo-vvseksperten.jpg"></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="band band-big-buttons pad" style="border-top:1px solid #D4D5D7;border-bottom:1px solid #D4D5D7">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="medium-6 columns">
			<a href="http://produkter.vvseksperten.no/?memberId=710" class="bb btn-1" target="_blank"> <i class="fa fa-folder-open fa-3x"></i><br>Åpne Produktliste<span>Kategorisert liste over alle produkter</span></a>	
		</div>
		<div class="medium-6 columns">
